        <obo:IAO_0000115 rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">A bipolar disorder in which at least one episode of major depression alternates with at least one episode of hypomania. In contrast to bipolar I disorder, affected individuals do not experience any manic episodes.</obo:IAO_0000115>
