        <obo:IAO_0000115 rdf:datatype="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#string">A non-neoplastic disorder that affects the gastrointestinal tract, anus, liver, biliary system, and pancreas. Representative examples include infections, ulcers, cirrhosis, and diverticulosis.</obo:IAO_0000115>
